# Streamlit App Walkthrough (Precision Mode)

## Summary
The finger mode is now set to **Very High Threshold** (0.25).

## Configuration
- **Threshold**: 0.25 (Very High).
- **Strike**: Requires a very fast, deliberate strike. This is the strictest setting to prevent accidental triggers.

## Mappings
| Hand | Finger | Natural (Straight) | Sharp (Curled) |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Left** | Pinky | C3 | C#3 |
| **Left** | Ring | D3 | D#3 |
| **Left** | Middle | E3 | F3 |
| **Left** | Index | F3 | F#3 |
| **Left** | Thumb | G3 | G#3 |
| **Right** | Thumb | A3 | A#3 |
| **Right** | Index | B3 | C4 |
| **Right** | Middle | C4 | C#4 |
| **Right** | Ring | D4 | D#4 |
| **Right** | Pinky | E4 | F4 |

## How to Run
```bash
./.venv/bin/streamlit run app.py
```
Open the URL shown in the terminal (usually http://localhost:8501).
